strings:
<voice_0x01001943><se_high>Mirrie: I didn't expect to see you in here today!
Heard something on the wind then, have you?

<voice_0x01001944><se_low>Morrie: Ah ha ha! Curioso, ay! I like that in my ladies!
(But not too much, eh, boys!? Ha ha, no...)
I come to see your face, Mirrie, my bellissimo flower!

<voice_0x01001945><se_high>Mirrie: Oh, you! Flattery will get you everywhere!
Tee hee!
<voice_0x01001946><se_low>Morrie: Ah ha ha! That's my girl!

<voice_0x01001947><se_low>Morrie: Va bene! It's this way!
I be waiting for you in the bottom!
